body:
The types should be as follows:

```
#if defined(__APPLE__)
static void sincos(double, double*, double*)  __attribute__((weakref ("__sincos")));
static void sincosf(float, float*, float*) __attribute__((weakref ("__sincosf")));
#endif
```
